data.description: OFFERING 2.4% BUYERS AGENT CO-OP. BEST VALUE IN U-HILLS.  JUST CALL 720-876-7454. Beautifully updated home in University Hills. This home is large and with 4 bedrooms and 2 baths its a rare find for the area. Enjoy the master suite at the back of the house for greater privacy. Bathrooms have been updated with the master bath featuring a walk in tile shower. The kitchen has been beautifully redone with handsome maple cabinets, tile floors, and stainless steel appliances. The back yard features a covered patio, large yard and mature trees. Other features and updates include hardwood floors, double pane windows, professional landscaping, sprinkler system, fenced yard, a roof less than 5 years old, and a large garden shed for extra storage. Located in the desirable University Hills subdivision, its an easy walk to parks, schools, shopping and more. With lots of extra space and updated interior, this house is truly an outstanding value!
